    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1><span id="html基础">HTML基础</span></h1><!-- toc --><ul><li><a href="#%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE">文本标签</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%B6%85%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5">超链接</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC">表格</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8">列表</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%A1%A8%E5%8D%95">表单</a><ul><li><a href="#type%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E5%80%BC">type属性值</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%A1%A8%E5%8D%95%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE">表单标签</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#%E6%9F%A5%E9%98%85%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3">查阅文档</a></li></ul><!-- tocstop --><h2><span id="文本标签">文本标签</span></h2><h2><span id="超链接">超链接</span></h2><h2><span id="表格">表格</span></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;table&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;th&gt;表头1&lt;/th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;th&gt;表头2&lt;/th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;td&gt;单元格1&lt;/td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;td&gt;单元格2&lt;/td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/table&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><span id="列表">列表</span></h2><p><strong>无序列表</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;列表1&lt;/li&gt; #&lt;ul&gt;里面只能放&lt;li&gt;标签，但&lt;li&gt;里面放什么都可以</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/ul&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>有序列表</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;ol&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;列表1&lt;/li&gt; #&lt;ol&gt;里面只能放&lt;li&gt;标签</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/ol&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>自定义列表</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;dl&gt; #&lt;dl&gt;里只能包含&lt;dt&gt;&lt;dd&gt;,&lt;dt&gt;等和上面一样</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;dt&gt;自定义列表1&lt;/dt&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;dd&gt;自定义列表1的描述&lt;/dd&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;dd&gt;自定义列表1的描述2&lt;/dd&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/dl&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><span id="表单">表单</span></h2><p>为了收集用户信息<br>在html中，一个完整的表单通常由表单域、表单控件（表单元素）和提示信息3部分组成<br><img src="/images/form1.png" alt="alt text"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;form action=&quot;submit.php&quot; method=&quot;post&quot; name=&quot;myForm&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;/form&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/form3.png" alt="alt text"><br><img src="/images/form2.png" alt="alt text"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;form&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    用户名:&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    密码:&lt;input type=&quot;password&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/form&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><span id="type属性值">type属性值</span></h3><ul><li>value只在文本框中能看到效果</li><li>name和value是每个表单元素都要有的属性，给后台人员使用</li><li>maxlength是用户可以在表单元素输入的最大字符数，一般较少使用</li><li>name是表单元素名，该处单选和复选必须有相同name,才可以实现多选一</li></ul><p><strong>单选和复选框</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#定义单选按钮 男&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;gender&quot; value=&quot;male&quot;&gt; 女&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;gender&quot; value=&quot;female&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#复选框 吃饭&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; name=&quot;act&quot; value=&quot;eat&quot;&gt; 睡觉&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; name=&quot;act&quot; value=&quot;sleep&quot;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>单选和复选框可以设置checked属性，默认选中</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">吃饭&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; name=&quot;act&quot; value=&quot;eat&quot; checked=&quot;checked&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#其实直接打checked也行(checked只有一个取值)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>submit按钮</strong><br>提交给后台服务器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;提交表单&quot;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>reset按钮</strong><br>重置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;input type=&quot;reset&quot; value=&quot;重新设置&quot;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>button按钮(不提交元素)</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;获取验证码&quot;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>文件域 用于上传文件</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">上传头像：&lt;input type=&quot;file&quot;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><span id="表单标签">表单标签</span></h3><p><strong>label标签</strong><br>为input元素定义标签，方便用户点击</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;label for=&quot;gender&quot;&gt;男&lt;/label&gt; for和id的值要一样</span><br><span class="line">&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;gender&quot; id=&quot;gender&quot; value=&quot;male&quot; /&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>select标签</strong><br>定义下拉列表<br>默认选中：selected&#x3D;”selected”(写selected即可,理由同checked)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">选择：</span><br><span class="line">&lt;select&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;option value=&quot;1&quot;&gt;选项1&lt;/option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;option value=&quot;2&quot;&gt;选项2&lt;/option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/select&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>textarea标签</strong><br>定义多行文本框(文本域)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">个性签名：</span><br><span class="line">&lt;textarea name=&quot;content&quot; rows=&quot;5&quot; cols=&quot;30&quot;&gt;请输入个性签名&lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#在实际开发中用css控制行列，忘了row和col吧</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><span id="查阅文档">查阅文档</span></h2><ol><li>W3school: <a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/">https://www.w3school.com.cn/</a></li><li>MDN:<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
